# Parity item #4: Search library = keyboard -> case-insensitive substring over the on-card stub
# mirror (the whole catalog) -> results with a system suffix -> the SAME gm_actions flow.
desc Search library: case-insensitive hit opens gm_actions for the mapped game
config paired
seeded
sdfile Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
sdfile+ Roms/Super Nintendo (SFC)/✓ Metroid.sfc
pick 0|Search library
kb 0|zEl
pick 0|✘ Zelda.gba  -  Game Boy Advance (GBA)
pick 0|Details
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace LIST[Search: zEl] rc=0
expect_trace LIST[Details] rc=2
